claim.claim-text:
1. A coupon booklet for use by a customer at a number of stores, said booklet comprising: 
a front cover and a back cover having a common edge; 
a number of pages each coupled to said common edge; 
a listing of a plurality of items entitled to discounts; and 
a single bar code identifying said plurality of items; 
wherein said front and back covers and said number of pages are coupled to said common edge such that said front and back cover and said number of pages are openable and closeable in a book-like manner.
